quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,"By the Day of Resurrection"
  75,2,"and by the self-reproaching soul!"
  75,3,"Does man think We shall not put his bones back together?"
  75,4,"In fact, We can reshape his very fingertips."
  75,5,"Yet man wants to deny what is ahead of him:"
  75,6,"he says, ‘So, when will this Day of Resurrection be?’"
  75,7,"When eyes are dazzled"
  75,8,"and the moon eclipsed,"
  75,9,"when the sun and the moon are brought together,"
  75,10,"on that Day man will say, ‘Where can I escape?’"